@AbapCatalog.viewEnhancementCategory: [#NONE]
@AccessControl.authorizationCheck: #NOT_REQUIRED
@EndUserText.label: 'Branch data'
@Metadata.ignorePropagatedAnnotations: true
@ObjectModel.usageType:{
    serviceQuality: #X,
    sizeCategory: #S,
    dataClass: #MIXED
}
define view entity /PYXS/NF_BRANCH as select from I_BR_BusinessPlace as b
    association [0..1] to I_AddlCompanyCodeInformation as cp on cp.CompanyCode = $projection.COD_COMPANHIA 
                          and cp.CompanyCodeParameterType = 'J_1BCG'
    association [0..1] to I_OrganizationAddress as addr on addr.AddressID = b.AddressID
                          
{   
    key b.CompanyCode as COD_COMPANHIA,
    key b.Branch as COD_ESTAB,
    b.BusinessPlaceName as RAZAO,
    replace(b.BusinessPlaceStateTaxNumber, '.', '') as INSCR_ESTADUAL,
    cp.CompanyCodeParameterValue as CNPJ_RAIZ,
    b.BR_BusinessPlacePartOfCNPJ as CNPJ_FILIAL,
    addr._Country.Country as CountryCode,
    addr._Country._Text[Language = 'P'].CountryName as CountryName,
    addr.Region as UF,
    addr._Region._RegionText[Language = 'P'].RegionName,
    substring( addr.TaxJurisdiction, 1, 3 ) as COD_IBGE,
    addr.CityName as MunicipioNome,
    b.BusPlaceMunicipalTaxNumber as INSCR_MUNICIPAL,
    b.BR_SUFRAMACode as INSCR_SUFRAMA,
    b.BusinessPlaceName as NOME_FANTASIA,
    addr.PostalCode as CEP,
    addr.StreetName as ENDERECO,
    addr.HouseNumber as NUMERO,
    addr.HouseNumberSupplementText as COMPLEMENTO,
    addr.DistrictName as BAIRRO,
    addr._PhoneNumber.InternationalPhoneNumber as TELEFONE,
    addr._EmailAddress.EmailAddress as EMAIL
}
